      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASH INTENTION (8) was well off top last time, finishing 5th (25.52) in a R/A FIN at Ballarat. Great record here at the trip having never missed the frame including one win. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. ASTON MORENO (6) steps out for the first time at this course. Scored last start (26.01) at Geelong over 460m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. One of the leading chances again. CASH IN VIEW (3) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 1.75 lengths (25.42) at this track. Should be in this for a long way. ASTON HARUTO (7) scored with plenty to spare last time. Must be respected.",
